HR NO. 248 ENROLLED
THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the House of Representatives of the
Legislature of Louisiana does hereby commend Michelle Woodfork on her election to the
office of sheriff of Orleans Parish; does hereby express appreciation for her leadership as
interim superintendent of the New Orleans Police Department; and does hereby extend
sincere wishes for continued success as she begins a new chapter in her law enforcement
career.
